    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Twelve pillars - As the altar was a symbol of the presence of Yahweh, so these twelve pillars represented the presence of the Twelve tribes with whom He was making the covenant. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
