      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Moses wrote all the words of the Lord",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". We may presume that they were miraculously brought to his remembrance by that Spirit of Truth which guided all the Prophets (",
